  "title": "Production Operator #79943",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Skin Care and Cosmetics Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Production Operator</strong></li><li>Working Location: North – Ang Mo Kio (Require taking few bus stops)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days / Mon-Fri: 8am-5pm, Sat 8am-12pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic SGD 1400 + Allowances + AWS + Variable Bonus + Medical & Dental Benefits</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Arrange and prepare raw materials and packaging materials for daily production according to schedule</li><li>Perform and fulfil daily production activities such as filling, capping, labelling, scooping, and packing finished products into cartons</li><li>Conduct weight checks and quality checks to ensure products meet company standards.</li><li>Load and unload goods onto pallets and prepare cartons with proper labelling</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of machines, production areas, clean rooms, and corridors, including mopping floors and disposing of rubbish</li><li>Assist the Production Supervisor with documentation and ensure smooth production flow</li><li>Work as a team to achieve daily output targets and support colleagues when needed</li><li>Follow all company and departmental safety rules and regulations</li><li>Report any damages, improvement suggestions, or purchase needs to the supervisor</li><li>Perform any other ad-hoc duties assigned by the Production Supervisor or Management</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. O level</li><li>Min. 1 year of working experience in the related field</li><li>Have chemistry background would be an added advantage</li><li>Comfortable working in clean room environment</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79943 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
